      • lookupCase

        protected Case lookupCase(java.lang.String caseIdentifier,
                          Rat rat)
        Returns the determined Case. First this method will try to find a case by the caseIdentifier. The caseIdentifier can be either the case number or the name of the client. If no case can be found by caseIdentifier it will try to find an open case with the given rat already assigned. If that does not work either the case will be guessed the latest added case of the same platform as the rat. If all fails null will be returned.
        Parameters:
        caseIdentifier - The case identifier to search for, can be null.
        rat - The rat to search for, can be null.
        Returns:
        the case as defined by the search criteria.
